4146.title: American Dad!
4146.description: Roger acts as the caretaker for a down and out shopping mall, desperately trying to keep the mall running while stores are dying out. When Steve arrives looking for a summer job, Roger hires him and the two try to find a way to revitalize the mall. As Roger and Steve finally find success in bringing back customers, Steve learns the mall's terrible secret. Meanwhile the rest of the family open a food truck business.

4167.title: American Dad!
4167.description: American Dad gaat over patriottische CIA-agent Stan Smith (stem door Seth Macfarlane) en de avonturen van z'n onconventionele gezin in Langley Falls, VA.

49363.title: American Dad!
49363.description: While Barry's parents are out of town, Steve and the boys pressure Barry into having a party. When they accidently break Barry's father's stereo, Barry and Snot set off on a journey to find new speakers. The journey leads them to a deranged music enthusiast, one of Roger's personas, who becomes obsessed with Barry. Meanwhile, Stan tries to pull off a back flip.

49384.title: American Dad!
49384.description: Stan is arrested for crashing into the C.I.A. flagpole and for community service he is assigned to assist Hayley with her Girl Scout troop. Stan's plan is to sleep through his service, but when he forms a bond with the girls, he pushes Hayley out and takes the troop over. Meanwhile Steve uses his rich imagination to escape the pressures of daily life, but the stress of the real world begins to break into his fantasies.
